  Name: Fra Raymond, knight of Justice
  Icon: {fileID: 1208347981, guid: b2407ce4cf73ad348aec15ba9990f7a1, type: 3}
  Description: 'He is the kind of noble who believes pain is beneath him. When a
    halberd hook tore under his arm and opened the axillary artery, arrogance evaporated.
    He is suddenly a man begging for heat and iron.


    Treatment: Tourniquet across
    shoulder fails to reach the artery. Heat the iron bright and press against the
    fountain. The scream is necessary. If bleeding stops, fever takes over.


    Requires:
    4 Bandages'
